Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:20.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... Very bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see. This is where they suck you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No... Run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.69,sign_1219_5_Miso_Natto_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Miso {\c&H0F2C28&}Natto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, not natto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:02.32,Default,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 363 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:07.67,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a grooved-edge ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:17.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:28.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:45.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess anyone's eyes would be tired after \Nholing up in their room, gaming all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:08.67,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.46,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This stuff obviously isn't fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.91,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.22,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So does this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:29.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been summoned into a parallel world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can assume this is a fantasy world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,with the typical medieval-style culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A realm where demihumans are commonplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and probably stuff like wars \Nand adventures, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And here, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.67,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:17.86,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the event where \NI produce my first magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.39,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.51,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.48,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:41.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not quite ready to use magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.39,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:48.46,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.74,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some weird clothes. \NAre you traveling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.17,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Those are appas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:59.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They understand me, though. \NThe question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:01.52,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What kind of money is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.66,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use that stuff in Lugunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.14,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're flat broke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.06,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here! \NDon't interfere with my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:15.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to go around \Ngathering information first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.32,Default,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,This place is for demihumans only.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! I can't... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how it's supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I summoned into a parallel world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd my protagonist status go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:56.19,sign_7096_50__Phone_Menu_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,[Phone Menu]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:56.19,sign_7096_51__1_Contacts__2_G,Text,0000,0000,0000,,(1)Contacts\N(2)Group Search\N(3)Abbreviations\N(4)New Contacts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:59.19,sign_7096_50_Contacts,Text,0000,0000,0000,,[Contacts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:59.19,sign_7096_51_City_Hall__Dad__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,City Hall \NDad \NMom \NPizza
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My cell phone still works...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.11,sign_7174_55_Out_of_Range,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Out of Range
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But what's the point in having it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And my starting gear is way too wimpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You need a more substantial welfare program
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to satisfy pressure-free \Ngeneration kids like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:14.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have Excalibur or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:21.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, if I was summoned, \Nwhere's the cute girl who summoned me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did she summon me only \Nto leave me here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is she finally here?! \NThe cute girl who summoned... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.61,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.52,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna get hurt, \Ncough up whatever you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, it's a compulsory event...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.55,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.41,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.82,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is {\i1}that{\i0} the cute girl who summoned me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.55,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Summoned? I dunno what you're \Ntalkin' about, but I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.65,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Live strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that didn't make you decide to be less \Nhostile toward me, by any chance, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:10.17,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it rained on our \Nparade and made things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.78,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just calm down, Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.76,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Since ancient times, it's the rule that anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.35,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,summoned into a parallel world \Nwill display supernatural powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:23.07,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll mow these guys down and make \Nthem fuel for my shining future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You lumps of EXP!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I ever hit someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect it to hurt {\i1}me{\i0} that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But this world is set up \Nso that I'll be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:42.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My adrenaline is surging! I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:46.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! It was all my fault! \NForgive me! Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.22,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Play games with us, will you?! Die, scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.52,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,And don't think it'll be painless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.66,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.02,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.86,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Stop now, and I'll let this slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So just graciously return what you stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.15,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,What we stole?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.34,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please. It's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.81,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on the other stuff, \Nbut I can't let you have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Be good and hand it over, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.51,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come to save this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What strange clothes he has...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:57.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If you asked me whether I had any \Nconnection to him, I'd have to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.98,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,Then you've got no business with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.52,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,If someone stole from you, \Nit was that brat who just ran by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.92,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That way! She ran that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... They don't seem to be lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.47,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But regardless of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't overlook what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.53,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Mess with us, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.73,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you can \Nuse magic! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:34.45,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can win when \Nit's two against one?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Two against one may be unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.08,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Two against two should make it fair, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.22,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,You're a user of the spiritual arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.34,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Back off now and \NI won't come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Decide quick. I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.75,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch! Next time I see \Nyou, I won't go easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.63,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Do anything to her, and I'll \Nhaunt you and your kin forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.02,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you'll have any kin if I do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.44,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:19.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,See? You averted your eyes because \Nyou have a guilty conscience!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my judgment was spot-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.60,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was just an \Ninstinctive male reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.62,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't sense any malice at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.42,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You be quiet, Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You know who stole my insignia \Nfrom me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:37.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry, but I don't \Nhave the slightest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.81,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:47.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Did I really just come around the long way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably hurry after her, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I could... help...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.57,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, you shouldn't have tried to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.86,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.12,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.41,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,He won't die. We'll just leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.16,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.38,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but I bet \Nyou'll still help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.43,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.71,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.75,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not! I am not going to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.54,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's even super cute when she's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.74,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a parallel world fantasy for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is my head on someone's lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.70,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:30.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know cute girls were this hairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that can't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.42,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a thoughtful arrangement we made
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you could at least feel \Nhappy until you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, don't talk in that high voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No sane guy confuses a cat \Nfor the main heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:49.47,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, making myself bigger was \Nworth it to see you so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.09,Default,Subabu,0000,0000,0000,,You stayed with me the whole \Ntime I was unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.48,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:03.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I had to stay because there \Nare things I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:08.49,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Healing your wounds and making Puck \Nyour pillow until you woke up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,were for my own benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:11.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So I need you to repay me in kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For such a normal favor, you're making \Nit sound like I really owe you big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.22,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:20.59,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You have some idea who \Nstole my insignia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Insignia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean one of those badge things \Nthat shows your affiliation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:28.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It has a jewel in the center,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and it's about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:34.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but no matter how many \Ntimes you ask me, I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I see. No helping that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:40.17,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But you've given me the information \Nthat you know nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.93,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and you gave me my answer, \Nin return for healing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:43.64,Default,subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm in a hurry, so I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.85,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Your wounds should be better now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:51.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but next time, don't do dangerous things, \Nlike wandering into deserted alleys alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:53.65,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not concerned. I'm just warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:57.76,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens to you again, \Nsaving you won't be of any benefit to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.36,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,so don't expect me to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.25,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about her. She's so insincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.04,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think badly of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Insincere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think this goes beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She was in such a hurry to find \Nwhat was stolen from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,yet she stopped to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:22.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And she even came up with that lame excuse \Nfor a favor so I wouldn't feel like I owed her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,even though I'm a total stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who lives like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,is gonna end up wasting their whole life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:42.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What? Just so you know, I can only spend \Njust a little more time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:44.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I sense you're being a tiny bit lenient...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that. You lost \Nsomething important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I remember her face, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:52.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I see her again, I'll know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.32,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're very strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.75,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I can't \Ndo anything to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank you. \NThat's why I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.68,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything deserving of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:11.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I've already received \Ncompensation for healing your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to help you for my own sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My objective is... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! One good deed per day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.95,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sense any malice. I think \Nyou can just accept his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.45,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,The more shields between yourself and \Nruffians, the better, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:34.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you want me around for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:37.00,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it, though. \NI can't do anything to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:14:01.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I talked big, but isn't this town too \Nhuge to find one little thing in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.76,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's the capital of Lugunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:06.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even know that, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.73,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We haven't \Nasked your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.41,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Should we all introduce ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce myself first, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not only am I clueless, \NI'm also broke beyond compare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.01,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,When that's all you say, \Nyou really do sound hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:30.21,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Puck! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:35.22,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's very unusual to see someone who \Ncan touch a spirit so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, following the usual pattern, \Na small island nation to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.54,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Lugunica is the easternmost \Nnation on our continental map.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There's no nation east of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No way, really? \NThere's nothing east of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:53.71,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea where you \Nare, you have no money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:56.47,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,you can't read, and you have \Nno one who can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.74,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You might be in an even more \Nprecarious position than me, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:01.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru... was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.49,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,But when I look at you this way, \Nyou look pretty well-built.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I do work out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:16.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For a shut-in who's gotta guard \Nhis house, that much is a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:19.03,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I understand \Nwhat a "shut-in" is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.81,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but that means you're from a \Nrespectable family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Your fingers, too. They're very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.24,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,They're evidence that you don't \Nlive like a peasant at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:32.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And your muscles don't look like \Nthe kind you gain by working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, anyway, I know your cat's name now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't heard yours yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:39.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.97,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.13,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Satella.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:49.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I have no family name. \NYou can just call me Satella.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:53.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Satella...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.44,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You have terrible taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:05.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to get back to asking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get the feeling that child is lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but what about our questioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's important too, but if she's \Nlost, we have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no place to talk after you saved me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but do you understand the position we're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:31.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:36.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,She's crying! Is she not, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do this with me, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your help, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle it on my own from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,after I help that little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm not who you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.20,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.70,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your mom and dad with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.10,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh... Don't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.76,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything to you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:12.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What I have here is one \Ngrooved-edge ten-yen coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:17.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I will now clutch it tightly in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Tight, tight, tight... like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And now... Imagine that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And this... is where the coin was hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare, so take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You got separated from your mom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me and \Nthis young lady here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find them for you in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When we do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,people who don't know us probably think \Nwe're a married couple and child, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:17:59.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:03.43,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,At best, I can't see you as anything \Nmore than her older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think I'm that \Nmuch younger than you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think we took a pretty long way around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:25.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but what benefit will you insist \Nthat you got out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:29.92,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy. Now we can continue our \Nsearch with our minds at ease, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:33.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why did you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were against the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I could say I just wanted \Nto show off my magic trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but that would be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:42.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, finding your insignia will \Nbe my one good deed for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:46.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Then, since you helped the little girl, \Nisn't your one good deed over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That comeback was way too logical!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:51.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it doesn't hurt to do more \Nthan one nice thing in a day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I just got tomorrow's out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My plan is to get a week's worth \Nof good deeds taken care of early!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:00.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, you're the type that basically \Nwastes your whole life, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last one I \Nwant saying that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.85,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a bad boy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you treating me like \NI'm younger than you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt there's that much \Ndifference between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.74,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think making guesses \Non that will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:27.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I thought you were so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Elves are always beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:37.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,"What"? Well, I mean... I'm a half-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:53.30,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I just had to do something about \Nthis unbearable tingle I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:56.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept being hit \Nfor a reason like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'll forgive you \Nbecause it was squishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.46,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hit you out of anger or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.01,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,The opposite, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, you're such a dunderhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Dunderhead? Who says that \Nin this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you insulting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.37,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:14.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we have \Nto get back to the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:20.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Running around without \Na plan never ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's a basic rule of searches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,A basic rule of searches?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:25.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. You revisit the crime \Nscene a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:27.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where was your insignia stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:30.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So you see, it seems the crime \Nhappened right around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:34.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,so I came back to this fruit stand after \Nvaliantly telling her to leave it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:37.88,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought I had a customer, \Nbut it's just the broke kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to take that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you noticed I'm \Nnot who I was before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.22,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just look who I brought with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:48.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I brought someone who just \Nmight become a regular!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.71,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have some \Nweird expectations of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have any money, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:03.24,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want to say to me now \Nthat I've got two broke customers, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually looking for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we hoped we could ask \Nyou some questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:11.90,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,That was a sarcastic way of telling you I \Ndon't have time for losers with no money!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.25,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:22.28,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's my husband's shop, \Nso we were just stopping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:31.06,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:35.42,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you know these broke losers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She got lost, and they found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.97,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Here, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.37,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to thank you in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.29,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.62,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:07.33,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,You helped my daughter, \Nand I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:08.62,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:13.03,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That came back around \Nand worked in our favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:36.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The air, the atmosphere, and most likely,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attitudes of the people \Nliving here are awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:44.28,Default - flashback,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that Felt girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.37,Default - flashback,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,You said a nimble little blond girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:50.93,Default - flashback,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,She's well-known in the slums. \NDunno where she lives, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.02,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone will tell us if we ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:58.80,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,No one would sell out one of their own, \Nso I don't think that would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:01.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:04.89,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you stay or leave, \Nyou should decide quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:06.74,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:08.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're what? Out of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:12.33,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I have a cute appearance, but I am a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:15.97,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,It take a lot of mana just \Nto appear in physical form.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:18.71,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,So at night, I return to \Nthe crystal I was summoned from
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and prepare for the \Nemergence of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:25.71,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,On average, my ideal staying time \Nis from about nine to five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:28.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nine to five? You sound \Nlike a civil servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:31.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Employment terms for spirits are \Nmore severe than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:34.68,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine without Puck. \NWe have to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:38.53,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But, sorry... I'm at my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:41.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like he's dying \Nwhen he disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.89,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to work you so hard, Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:46.81,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,We'll handle things from \Nhere, so get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:52.12,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:55.31,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes down to it, \Nuse the odo to summon me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:58.82,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, take care of the rest, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:13.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I haven't been alone with a \Ngirl since I was in grade school!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:16.06,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any weird ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.06,0:24:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.67,0:24:19.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:22.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger issue is how \Nwe should find Felt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask the lesser spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:26.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Lesser spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.62,0:24:30.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Lesser spirits are beings that \Nhaven't become spirits yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.90,0:24:34.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,They grow over time, and when they \Ngain strength and self-awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.56,0:24:36.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,they become full spirits, like Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
